body:
### Welcome to SPHERO.
Sphero is currently a work in progress.  Updates on pre-release and Beta testing will be released soon.


### Authors and Contributors
Sphero was created and designed by Anton Solomonik (@xerxesv), Jordan Olthoff (@jolthoff), Rodrigo Delgado (@rdalcega), and Zachary Castellanos-Smith (@ztsmith25).

### Support or Contact
Have questions or want to contribute? Check out our [documentation](https://github.com/EuphoniousTrapezoid/euphonious_trapezoid).
